      "text": "Official exam context"
    },
    {
      "id": "n20",
      "type": "heading",
      "order": 19,
      "level": 2,
      "text": "What the Goethe B1 Exam Checks"
    },
    {
      "id": "n21",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 20,
      "text": "Goethe-Zertifikat B1 confirms independent German skills at CEFR B1 for young people and adults."
    },
    {
      "id": "n22",
      "type": "heading",
      "order": 21,
      "level": 3,
      "text": "Exam format and timing"
    },
    {
      "id": "n23",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 22,
      "text": "The exam has listening, reading, writing, and speaking modules. The four modules can be taken individually or in combination."
    },
    {
      "id": "n24",
      "type": "heading",
      "order": 23,
      "level": 4,
      "text": "Listening"
    },
    {
      "id": "n25",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 24,
      "text": "40 minutes"
    },
    {
      "id": "n26",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 25,
      "text": "Announcements, short lectures, informal conversations, and radio discussions."
    },
    {
      "id": "n27",
      "type": "heading",
      "order": 26,
      "level": 4,
      "text": "Reading"
    },
    {
      "id": "n28",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 27,
      "text": "65 minutes"
    },
    {
      "id": "n29",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 28,
      "text": "Blog posts, emails, newspaper articles, advertisements, and written instructions."
    },
    {
      "id": "n30",
      "type": "heading",
      "order": 29,
      "level": 4,
      "text": "Writing"
    },
    {
      "id": "n31",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 30,
      "text": "60 minutes"
    },
    {
      "id": "n32",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 31,
      "text": "Personal and formal emails or letters plus a written forum opinion."
    },
    {
      "id": "n33",
      "type": "heading",
      "order": 32,
      "level": 4,
      "text": "Speaking"
    },
    {
      "id": "n34",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 33,
      "text": "15 minutes"
    },
    {
      "id": "n35",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 34,
      "text": "Planning with a partner, responding to questions, giving opinions, making suggestions, and presenting a current topic."
    },
    {
      "id": "n36",
      "type": "heading",
      "order": 35,
      "level": 3,
      "text": "Best for"
    },
    {
      "id": "n37",
      "type": "heading",
      "order": 36,
      "level": 4,
      "text": "Independent everyday German"
    },
    {
      "id": "n38",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 37,
      "text": "Useful for work, school, travel, leisure, opinions, and simple explanations."
    },
    {
      "id": "n39",
      "type": "heading",
      "order": 38,
      "level": 4,
      "text": "Settlement and citizenship preparation"
    },
    {
      "id": "n40",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 39,
      "text": "Relevant for routes where an authority asks for B1 German. Check local certificate rules before booking."
    },
    {
      "id": "n41",
      "type": "heading",
      "order": 40,
      "level": 3,
      "text": "How to use your practice time"
    },
    {
      "id": "n42",
      "type": "list",
      "order": 41,
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        {
          "text": "Familiar topics from work, school, travel, leisure, and personal interests."
        },
        {
          "text": "Giving reasons and short explanations for opinions and plans."
        },
        {
          "text": "Writing feedback for structure, register, clarity, and task completion."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "n43",
      "type": "heading",
      "order": 42,
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Frequently Asked Questions"
    },
    {
      "id": "n44",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 43,
      "text": "Everything you need to know about the exam!"
    },
    {
      "id": "n45",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 44,
      "text": "B1 is the common target when an authority asks for independent German language skills for naturalization or settlement permit."
    },
    {
      "id": "n46",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 45,
      "text": "Yes. Goethe-Institut describes B1 as modular, so listening, reading, writing, and speaking can be taken individually or together."
    },
    {
      "id": "n47",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 46,
      "text": "Many learners struggle with writing structure, speaking fluency, and giving clear reasons for opinions."
    },
    {
      "id": "n48",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 47,
      "text": "Last reviewed: May 2026. This page is independent exam preparation. For official registration, fees, dates, and accepted certificate rules, check the exam provider and the institution or authority requesting your certificate."
    }
